research/history/logs/agent_round_0155.stdout.log:4371:research/history/logs/agent_round_0139.stdout.log:2346:research/history/logs/agent_round_0130.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_perf_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是 shared low-rank projection，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库；在线链路仍可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + 单 expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 仍属直接兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r129 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，在保持 `K=128`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 不变时，shared 分支已覆盖全局主干，routed 分支可以收缩到单 expert 而不显著伤害 FVU，从而把 selection cost 从约 0.24x 压到约 0.16x、total_cost 从约 0.37x 压到约 0.29x，并直接回答这条“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local top-k”异构 MoE 线是否能形成新的 <0.3x Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 在约 0.29x 下仍接近 r129 的 FVU，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192` 或 `128`，继续压 shared scorer 成本。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显掉点，则说明该 family 的瓶颈更像 routed capacity 而非 active path 过长；下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 做 matched-cost 对照，而不是回到旧 family。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `active_experts=1` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 AutoResearch override allowlist；此前该 family 对 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` / `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` / `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 的 param-only probe 会在训练前被判为 disallowed。","本地校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides(..., fallback_architecture='shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk')` 现在接受 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，同时仍拒绝不属于该 family 的 `TRUNK_RANK`。","exact smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward；成本自检为 selection≈0.16x、deploy≈0.12x、total≈0.29x。"],"reference_round":129,"self_review":"这轮先消除真实 blocker：r129 之后该新 family 虽已可训练，但 AutoResearch 没把它接到 expert/factorized override allowlist，导致后续单变量结构 probe 无法合法发起。真实落盘改动只在 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`，不改 trainer/eval 语义；计划运行时相对 r129 仍只改 1 个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`。风险是单 expert 路由可能让 FVU 回退到被现有 0.30x-0.34x anchor 支配；但这正是当前低开销阶段最需要回答的结构问题。","summary":"已落盘修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 override 接线，使这条新异构 MoE family 可以继续做合法的单变量 param-only 探针。建议本轮以 r129 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，用一次 matched-cost 低开销实验直接检验“shared low-rank basis + 单 routed expert local top-k”是否能把该 family 推进到新的 <0.3x Pareto 段。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
