research/history/logs/agent_round_0155.stdout.log:4551:research/history/logs/agent_round_0142.stdout.log:598:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,j}(h(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，{b_i^sh} 是 shared 静态向量库，{b_{e,j}} 是 routed expert 静态子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r123 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“shared+routed 异构 MoE 中把 expert 内部 scorer 也做低秩化”是否能在约 0.22x total_cost 下形成新的低成本结构段。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.22x 下明显优于现有 0.22x-0.25x frontier，则下一轮保持该 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，继续压缩 hetero MoE 的低秩路由链路。","如果该点仍明显落后于当前 low-cost frontier，则可以更有把握地下调“fully factorized hetero MoE”优先级，把后续预算转向其他结构槽位，而不是继续在 shared+routed 低秩变体上反复试错。","如果结果只小幅优于 `expert_topk` 但仍被 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 支配，则说明 shared branch 有价值，但 routed experts 过度低秩化会伤害质量；后续应优先保留 expert-specific full heads 或切向别的 staged/residual 结构。"],"notes_to_memory":["r141 已说明 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 在约 0.30x total_cost 下仍被当前 low-cost frontier 压制，因此“shared low-rank basis + full expert head”这条无 residual 线可暂时降级。","本轮改做另一条 hetero MoE 结构对照：相对 r123 只切 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，用同一低成本 anchor 直接测试 expert 内部低秩 scorer 是否值得继续。","本地成本自检：在 r123 配方下切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 后，selection_accesses=450560、deployment_accesses=458752、combined_accesses=909312，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.22，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":123,"self_review":"这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r123 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 连续两轮非支配失败、`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 也已给出新的负信号后，继续沿同一 family 做局部压缩信息增量偏低；切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 更符合当前对异构 MoE 与 expert-internal low-rank 的优先级，也能在更低的 0.22x 成本带补一段此前仍欠清晰的结构证据。主要风险是该 family 在旧轮次已有弱负信号，但当前这次是与 r123 严格 matched-cost 的 fresh validation，结论更有解释力。","summary":"建议以 r123 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`。这是一轮低成本异构 MoE 结构重验：直接测试“shared+routed + expert 内部低秩 scorer”能否在约 0.22x total_cost 下提供比当前 low-cost frontier 更有价值的新段。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0155.stdout.log:4552:research/history/logs/agent_action_0130.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_perf_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是 shared low-rank projection，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库；在线链路仍可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + 单 expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 仍属直接兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r129 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，在保持 `K=128`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 不变时，shared 分支已覆盖全局主干，routed 分支可以收缩到单 expert 而不显著伤害 FVU，从而把 selection cost 从约 0.24x 压到约 0.16x、total_cost 从约 0.37x 压到约 0.29x，并直接回答这条“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local top-k”异构 MoE 线是否能形成新的 <0.3x Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 在约 0.29x 下仍接近 r129 的 FVU，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192` 或 `128`，继续压 shared scorer 成本。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显掉点，则说明该 family 的瓶颈更像 routed capacity 而非 active path 过长；下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 做 matched-cost 对照，而不是回到旧 family。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `active_experts=1` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 AutoResearch override allowlist；此前该 family 对 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` / `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` / `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 的 param-only probe 会在训练前被判为 disallowed。","本地校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides(..., fallback_architecture='shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk')` 现在接受 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，同时仍拒绝不属于该 family 的 `TRUNK_RANK`。","exact smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward；成本自检为 selection≈0.16x、deploy≈0.12x、total≈0.29x。"],"reference_round":129,"self_review":"这轮先消除真实 blocker：r129 之后该新 family 虽已可训练，但 AutoResearch 没把它接到 expert/factorized override allowlist，导致后续单变量结构 probe 无法合法发起。真实落盘改动只在 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`，不改 trainer/eval 语义；计划运行时相对 r129 仍只改 1 个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`。风险是单 expert 路由可能让 FVU 回退到被现有 0.30x-0.34x anchor 支配；但这正是当前低开销阶段最需要回答的结构问题。","summary":"已落盘修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 override 接线，使这条新异构 MoE family 可以继续做合法的单变量 param-only 探针。建议本轮以 r129 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，用一次 matched-cost 低开销实验直接检验“shared low-rank basis + 单 routed expert local top-k”是否能把该 family 推进到新的 <0.3x Pareto 段。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
