research/history/logs/agent_round_0155.stdout.log:4575:research/history/logs/agent_round_0141.stdout.log:533:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 是 routed expert 静态子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r123 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 与其余训练配方不变，直接做一次 matched-cost hetero-MoE 结构对照，回答“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local head”这条线在约 0.30x total_cost 下是否能形成比当前 low-cost anchor 更有价值的新结构段。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.30x 下明显优于现有 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 邻近锚点，则下一轮保持该 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 继续压低 shared/routed 成本。","如果该点仍被当前 0.28x-0.30x frontier 支配，则可更明确地下调“无 residual 的 shared-lowrank+routed”优先级，把后续预算转回别的结构槽位，而不是继续在这条 family 上做局部扫参。","如果结果介于 r123 与当前 0.30x anchor 之间，则说明 shared low-rank basis 有一定价值但单独不足以形成新段；后续应优先考虑带 residual 的版本或新的 staged expert 结构，而不是再压同一 recipe。"],"notes_to_memory":["r139-r140 已说明 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 连续两轮未形成新非支配点；本轮按策略切回新的结构假设对照，而不是继续沿同一 family 做局部压缩。","本轮不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做旧 family 局部微调，而是以当前低成本 reference r123 为 matched baseline，直接重验更符合当前 agenda 的 hetero MoE 结构 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。","本地成本自检：在 r123 配方下切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 后，selection_accesses=794624、deployment_accesses=458752、combined_accesses=1253376，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.30，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":123,"self_review":"这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r123 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 已连续两轮未形成新非支配点后，继续沿同一 family 做 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `K` 的局部扫参信息增量偏低；切回 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 做 matched-cost architecture swap，更符合当前“结构扩展优先”和对 hetero MoE 的明确优先级。主要风险是该 family 先前在更高容量配方下已有负信号；但当前这次是更低成本、与 low-cost anchor 严格对照的重验，结论会更清晰。","summary":"建议以 r123 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。这是一轮面向低成本前沿的 matched-cost 结构对照，用当前最相关的 low-cost anchor 直接回答“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local top-k”是否值得继续，而不是继续在最近连续失利的 residual 变体上做局部压缩。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0155.stdout.log:4576:research/history/logs/agent_action_0138.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{l∈S_res(r1(x))} γ_l(x) c_l，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，r1(x)=x-Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i-Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}；U={u_i} 是静态 shared low-rank library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库，C={c_l} 是静态 residual library。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“shared low-rank projection + 少量 routed experts 选择 + 静态库查表加权和 + 选择性 residual 补偿”，不依赖动态生成字典，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：当前最有信息量但尚无最小原型的槽位，不是再扫现有 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 hidden/K 邻域，而是给这条 hetero MoE 线补上一段全局 residual cleanup。相对 r134 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“shared low-rank basis + routed experts + residual cleanup”能否在约 0.60x total_cost 的中低成本带形成新的 Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该新 family 在约 0.60x 下明显优于 r134 且接近当前中成本最优点，则下一轮优先修好该 architecture 的 override allowlist，然后只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，区分瓶颈是在 stage1 shared+routed 容量还是 residual cleanup 配额。","如果该点有正信号但成本偏重，则下一轮在接好 allowlist 后只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 之一，测试 hetero MoE + residual 能否继续左移。","如果该点明显弱于 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 或只小幅优于 r134，则可较清晰判定 residual 增益不足以抵消 shared+routed 的额外复杂度，后续应把预算转回别的兼容结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，真实改动仅落在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py