research/history/logs/agent_round_0155.stdout.log:4773:research/history/logs/agent_round_0129.stdout.log:1049:research/history/results.tsv:128:r127_1774834186	1774834186	ok	discard	0.22480779886245728	128	shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk	1				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0127/round0127_standard_1774833792_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k128_20260330_092318	3ebb6b42987441ba9d13373ca8ce6cb5ea3684cd			已实际落盘新的 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 最小原型，并完成 instantiate/forward/backward 本地 smoke。以 r108 为 matched reference，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 切到这个新 family，直接验证“异构 shared+routed MoE + shared low-rank basis + expert-local top-k”是否值得继续。	这轮不再把主要预算投入到现有 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的局部扫参，符合当前额外提示。代码改动限制在 `sparsify/`，没有新增 env key，也没有改执行层；新 family 复用现有 `NUM_EXPERTS / ACTIVE_EXPERTS / LATENTS_PER_EXPERT / FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 语义。为降低工程风险，我只实现最小注册链与前向/反向路径，并用 `architecture=shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk, K=128, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 完成了本地 instantiate/forward/backward smoke。主要风险是该 family 虽然 scorer 更轻，但 shared low-rank basis 可能削弱 shared+routed 的表达能力；不过这正是当前最需要回答的新结构问题。	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0127_standard_1774833792.log
research/history/logs/agent_round_0155.stdout.log:4774:research/history/logs/agent_round_0129.stdout.log:1050:research/history/results.tsv:129:r128_1774834662	1774834662	ok	discard	0.22480779886245728	128	shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk	1				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0128/round0128_standard_1774834298_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k128_20260330_093144	ccbcc6eb92b69bc663b8407be38c57c97e11db41			先不给新 family做局部扫参，直接做首轮 matched architecture swap。以 r108 为 reference，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 切到刚集成并已 smoke 通过的 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，验证这条异构 MoE + shared low-rank basis 新结构是否值得继续。	满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r108 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不再继续沿 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做局部邻域延长，符合当前运行时优先级；也不新增 env key，因此无需改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。选择 r108 而不是更近的 r121-r123，是因为 r108 提供了当前新 family 最干净的 matched shared+routed recipe，且 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320, K=128, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 已被证明是可行的强基线。主要风险是 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 的 shared basis 可能损失过多表达能力；但这正是当前最需要的新结构证据。	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0128_standard_1774834298.log
