research/history/logs/agent_round_0155.stdout.log:4811:research/history/logs/agent_round_0129.stdout.log:2291:research/history/logs/agent_action_0128.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":108,"family_name":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，shared 子库与各 routed expert 子库都是真正静态向量库，因此在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared low-rank projection + shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和”流水线；兼容性判断为直接兼容。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是不兼容，只能作历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：当前额外提示已明确要求停止把主要预算继续投入现有 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的局部扫参，而优先验证新的异构 MoE 结构信息；因此应先对刚完成集成的新 family 做一次最干净的 matched-cost 首轮验证。相对 r108 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`EF=1`、`adam`、`8e-4` 不变，直接回答“shared+routed experts + shared low-rank basis + expert-local top-k”是否能在相近或更低 total_cost 下优于现有 shared+routed 线。按当前成本模型，这个结构应主要压低 encoder selection 成本，而 deployment 成本与 r108 同量级，因此有机会在 <0.5x 带形成新的结构性前沿。","summary":"先不给新 family做局部扫参，直接做首轮 matched architecture swap。以 r108 为 reference，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 切到刚集成并已 smoke 通过的 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，验证这条异构 MoE + shared low-rank basis 新结构是否值得继续。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r108 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不再继续沿 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做局部邻域延长，符合当前运行时优先级；也不新增 env key，因此无需改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。选择 r108 而不是更近的 r121-r123，是因为 r108 提供了当前新 family 最干净的 matched shared+routed recipe，且 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320, K=128, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 已被证明是可行的强基线。主要风险是 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 的 shared basis 可能损失过多表达能力；但这正是当前最需要的新结构证据。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 已在 `sparsify/config.py` 和 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` 实际落盘，并完成 instantiate/forward/backward 本地 smoke。","新 family 复用已有 tunables `NUM_EXPERTS`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，没有新增 env key。","本轮是对新增 family 的首个 matched validation，不应在首轮同时改 `K`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 或 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，否则无法清晰归因。","如果首轮结果异常，应先区分是训练稳定性问题还是结构负信号，而不要重新归因为注册链问题。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果新 family 在相近或更低 total_cost 下明显优于 r108，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=96`，测试这条新结构能否继续向更低 deployment 成本左移。","如果新 family有正信号但仍弱于预期，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，区分瓶颈是在 shared basis 宽度还是在 expert capacity。","如果新 family明显不如 matched `shared_routed_expert_topk`，则可较清晰判定当前 target 上这类异构 MoE 的 low-rank scorer 还不足以抵消表示损失，后续应切回别的未充分验证结构槽位，而不是继续细扫该 family。"]}
